{"tid":465403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【風韻猶荃】汪 明 荃 身 穿 性 感 中 門 大 開 deep V 晚 裝 艷 壓 全 場","createTime":"2017-11-11T13:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T13:57:10.000Z","uid":24160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c979a20c5672c23996efe947829b60eec6f2281b","tid":465403,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T13:42:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tipEIQV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtipEIQV.jpg&h=f738b427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪明荃博士身穿黑色&quot;中門大開&quot;晚裝乘坐駕進入半島酒店會場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LQUjBgI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLQUjBgI.jpg&h=a76b6636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪博士更與一眾司儀合照，眾人服飾顯得汪氏晚裝簡約而高貴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LBIifFH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLBIifFH.jpg&h=21c05f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪氏與王浩信合照<br />\n此照更能清楚觀察到汪氏事業線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dsfgXjx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdsfgXjx.jpg&h=aaf3f200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CUT4Wr6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCUT4Wr6.jpg&h=d28bccb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n王浩信難抵阿姐魅力<br />\n害羞得不敢側目凝視<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5XfaCT8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5XfaCT8.jpg&h=bcd5454c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪氏換上另一套米色晚裝，盡顯其玲瓏身段<br />\n企喺上等人及一眾甘草演員旁<br />\n更後生成廿年有多，唔似七十歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CPu4OmM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCPu4OmM.jpg&h=fa0a294b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n及後，汪氏再換上閃爆護肩低胸晚裝保護其隨歲月而退化嘅肩膀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其閃爍裝飾簡直閃爆所有重量級嘉賓, 包括胡定欣, Miss Chan Chan, 容祖祖等人<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NydEpPv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNydEpPv.jpg&h=4f2b85b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aThh6jS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaThh6jS.jpg&h=f1a6bcdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/4_img/upload/d411fbc6/20171111/l0eo-fynstfh4874445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2F4_img%2Fupload%2Fd411fbc6%2F20171111%2Fl0eo-fynstfh4874445.jpg&h=ce69249e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪氏亦曾身穿紅色高叉晚裝進出會場<br />\n右邊男子為曾向汪氏問價之高層<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/540/https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/mw690/6776b853gy1fka5xap6cqj20zk0qoaji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F6776b853gy1fka5xap6cqj20zk0qoaji.jpg&h=f064a680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿姐真係忙一日換幾套衫<br />\n<br />\n號外容祖兒下身所穿嘅係高叉裙<br />\n氣勢絕不比汪氏輪蝕<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/29nBZAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F29nBZAH.jpg&h=82b34ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 七十明荃 風韻猶存<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊重溫阿姐演唱會之風采 [5分鐘精華]<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/INS26vhNJdQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FINS26vhNJdQ&d=xgxmiVok%2BgQon%2BgoicWuyzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=27a38f07\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/INS26vhNJdQ</a></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SmHL0LV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSmHL0LV.gif&h=c841f8ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/inRBfIw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FinRBfIw.gif&h=7372f518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0YaORci.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0YaORci.gif&h=3ed32585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/JMq7bOi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJMq7bOi.gif&h=36fa2dd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/11-28-2015/lA5WNN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F11-28-2015%2FlA5WNN.gif&h=92700877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</div></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"1369788386b2708f26029eec7a0d8a48bec0f3e6","tid":465403,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T13:45:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac52b52396599419e5bc7efc0314e43db4860c22","tid":465403,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T13: